# mock

Mock implementations for `{{ .Name }}` tests.

Place generated or hand-written mocks here. Recommended tools:

- `mockgen` (from `go.uber.org/mock`) — generate from interfaces in `internal/server/service` and `internal/server/repository`
- `moq` — lightweight alternative with struct-based mocks

Example:
```
mockgen -source=internal/server/service/user_service.go -destination=mock/user_service_mock.go
```
